--- !u!1001 &781259856
PrefabInstance:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  serializedVersion: 2
  m_Modification:
    serializedVersion: 3
    m_TransformParent: {fileID: 837184287}
    m_Modifications:
    - target: {fileID: 1904170443898677983, guid: 5b8346b382fa5714aab15554b04b3c92,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_text
      value: 'explenation:

        If you die in a killbrick and there is something
        above you, you respawn either ontop of it or next to it. If you hit a killbrick
        with your head, you get a little height at spawn, and you clip into a block.

        If
        you are in a block, you can get your hitbox to clip to the top giving you
        a tiny bit more jump height'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
